UI for the raw data view.

Source: R/qda_view_module.R
qda_view_ui.Rd

This will display at tab group for each table in the qda() data object.

Usage

qda_view_ui(id, download_xlsx = TRUE, download_rda = TRUE)

Arguments

id

An ID string that corresponds with the ID used to call the module's UI function.

download_xlsx

include a download Excel button.

download_rda

include a download R data button.
